headline: Texas Instruments board declares first quarter 2026 quarterly dividend
summary: The board of directors of Texas Instruments Incorporated (Nasdaq: TXN) today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.42 per share of common stock, payable Feb. 10, 2026, to stockholders of record on Jan. 30, 2026.

headline: Microchip, Analog Devices target raised ahead of semiconductor earnings
summary: Investing.com --Wolfe Research raised estimates on select semiconductor names ahead of the fourth-quarter earnings season, arguing that while demand visibility remains mixed across end markets, downside risks appear limited and company-specific drivers are becoming more important.
